relicDescription: NSLOCTEXT("[FEA8EFE747B6BFEF48AD2AB3CBEF2B13]", "7A90B34D4A02CD58BC5DF4BE37485893", "The fat bole of a Sujomman Bobe forms the heart of Tumok\'s Totem. Scraped and scarred by the vast distances, and unnumbered hardships that Tumok has faced since leaving his homelands, the hardy bobe-trunk remains sturdy and firm. Only a few short branches afford the attachment of fetishes and baubles, collected along Tumok\'s long travels.")
name: Relic_Epic_Tumok_Totem
